{"code":200,"message":"成功","flag":true,"data":{"prId":54702766,"scoringMethod":1,"name":null,"exerList":[{"exerID":4326096,"title":"“生活中从不缺少美，而是缺少发现美的眼睛。”从马克思主义哲学的角度，对这句话的正确理解是（ ）。","courseID":"H011901","catID":943791,"optNum":4,"a":"客观事物的存在取决于主体的感知","b":"非理性因素在感性认识中起决定性作用","c":"认识是主体与客体相互作用的过程和结果","d":"人的感觉器官的选择性是人的认识能力的界限","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"C","keyType":"单选","analyze":"认识是主体与客体相互作用的产物，主体与客体在认识活动中的统一是以信息为媒介的。主体认识客体就是主体通过一定手段从客体中获取信息，并经过选择、加工、改造、变换、组织，在主体头脑中建构出一个与现实客体具有同构异质关系的观念客体的过程。故选C。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":37116,"correctTimesAmount":24110,"accuracyAmount":65.0,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":null,"newKeyType":1,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":1,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["C"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"单选","prname":"第一部分 马克思主义哲学原理>第四章 实践与认识及其发展规律","exerNum":null},{"exerID":4326097,"title":"美国宇航局（NASA）公布重磅消息：天文学家发现了迄今最像地球的系外行星——开普勒—452b。这颗行星与地球相似度之高，被形象地称为地球的“大表哥”。人类此次发现开普勒—452b，以及早前发现一系列地球“表亲”，都得益于开普勒太空望远镜从2009年升空到现在，这个以天文学家约翰内斯·开普勒命名的望远镜已经发现了超过一千颗系外行星。而据NASA专家预计，“开普勒”号可以在银河系中发现50颗以上的类地行星。这一事例告诉人们，认识的客体是（ ）。","courseID":"H011901","catID":943791,"optNum":4,"a":"主体创造出来的对象","b":"一切客观事物","c":"包括外太空在内的全部自然界","d":"主体认识活动所指向的对象","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"D","keyType":"单选","analyze":"实践客体与客观存在的事物不完全等同，客观事物只有在被纳入主体实践活动的范围之内，为主体实践活动所指向并与主体相互作用时才成为现实的实践客体，B、C错误，D正确。题干中的行星等都是客观存在的事物，不是主体创造出来的对象，A错误。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":36962,"correctTimesAmount":22473,"accuracyAmount":60.8,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":null,"newKeyType":1,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":2,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["D"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"单选","prname":"第一部分 马克思主义哲学原理>第四章 实践与认识及其发展规律","exerNum":null},{"exerID":4326098,"title":"恩格斯在谈到欧洲文艺复兴时期自然科学的迅速发展时指出：“资产阶级为了发展工业生产，需要科学来查明自然物体的物理特性，弄清自然力的作用方式。”这段话说明（ ）。","courseID":"H011901","catID":943791,"optNum":4,"a":"实践是认识发展的动力","b":"认识对实践具有相对独立性","c":"实践是检验认识是否具有真理性的标准","d":"认识对实践具有决定作用","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"A","keyType":"单选","analyze":"实践是认识发展的动力。实践的需要推动认识的产生和发展，推动人类的科学发现和技术发明，推动人类的思想进步和理论创新。A正确，B、C本身正确但不符合题意实践对认识具有决定作用，D说法错误。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":36985,"correctTimesAmount":17422,"accuracyAmount":47.1,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":null,"newKeyType":1,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":3,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["A"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"单选","prname":"第一部分 马克思主义哲学原理>第四章 实践与认识及其发展规律","exerNum":null},{"exerID":4326099,"title":"“批判的武器当然不能代替武器的批判，物质力量只能用物质力量来摧毁；但是理论一经群众掌握，也会变成物质力量。”这句话反映了（ ）","courseID":"H011901","catID":943791,"optNum":4,"a":"理论对实践具有指导作用","b":"理论不能代替实践","c":"理论本身就是物质的力量","d":"理论的作用可以通过实践表现出来","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"ABD","keyType":"多选","analyze":"本题考查实践与认识的关系。题干通过批判的武器（理论）和武器的批判（实践）的关系来论证理论和实践的辩证统一关系。理论是人们实践的结果，对实践具有指导作用，选项A、D正确；理论不是认识和实践的终点，形成和掌握理论是为了更好地实践，是为实践服务，指导实践，以满足人们生活和生产的需要，所以理论不能代替实践，选项B正确。选项C表述错误。因此，选项A、B、D正确。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":36878,"correctTimesAmount":14144,"accuracyAmount":38.4,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":0.0,"newKeyType":2,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":4,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["ABD"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"多选","prname":"第一部分 马克思主义哲学原理>第四章 实践与认识及其发展规律","exerNum":null},{"exerID":4326100,"title":"牛顿是一位伟大的科学家，他取得了巨大成就，走在时代前列，为全人类揭示了宇宙的本质和演化规律，但这些都离不开前人的智慧。所以他曾经说过：“假若我能比别人瞭望得略为远些，那是因为我站在巨人们的肩膀上。”这句话说明（ ）","courseID":"H011901","catID":943791,"optNum":4,"a":"认识具有历史继承性","b":"实践不是认识的唯一来源","c":"间接经验对认识发展有重要作用","d":"间接经验与直接经验无关","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"AC","keyType":"多选","analyze":"由于单个主体的生命和能力是有限的，不可能事事亲身实践，而且理论或认识本身也具有历史继承性，所以，主体可以也应该通过读书或传授等方式来获得间接经验，这是发展人类认识的必要途径。但是间接经验归根到底也是来源于前人或他人的实践，而且人们接受间接经验也要或多或少地以某种直接经验即实践为基础。只有把间接经验和直接经验结合起来，才能有比较完全的知识。因此，选项A、C正确。选项B，说法错误，马克思主义认为，实践是认识的唯一来源，无论是直接经验还是间接经验，都来自于实践，故不选。选项D，直接经验和间接经验是“源”与“流”的关系，它们都来自于实践，所以“间接经验与直接经验无关”这一说法是错误的，故不选。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":36806,"correctTimesAmount":17148,"accuracyAmount":46.6,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":0.0,"newKeyType":2,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":5,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["AC"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"多选","prname":"第一部分 马克思主义哲学原理>第四章 实践与认识及其发展规律","exerNum":null},{"exerID":4326101,"title":"下列选项中，正确说明真理与谬误关系的有（ ）。","courseID":"H011901","catID":943791,"optNum":4,"a":"在一定范围内真理和谬误是对立的","b":"真理和谬误相比较而存在","c":"真理和谬误相斗争而发展","d":"真理和谬误相互包含","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"ABC","keyType":"多选","analyze":"真理和谬误相互依存，没有真理也没有谬误，没有谬误也无所谓真理，二者相比较而存在，相斗争而发展。真理和谬误在一定范围内的对立是绝对的，但超出一定范围，它们就会互相转化，真理变成谬误，谬误变成真理。故ABC项符合题意。D项混淆了真理和谬误的界限。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":36617,"correctTimesAmount":18752,"accuracyAmount":51.2,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":0.0,"newKeyType":2,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":6,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["ABC"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"多选","prname":"第一部分 马克思主义哲学原理>第四章 实践与认识及其发展规律","exerNum":null},{"exerID":4326102,"title":"列宁也曾以玻璃杯子为例，说明一个物体在不同的人的不同使用中表现出多种不同的价值。同样，药物的价值是治疗疾病，它对病人有价值，对健康人则没有价值。以下说法正确的是（ ）。","courseID":"H011901","catID":943791,"optNum":4,"a":"价值离不开主体的需要，也离不开客体的特性","b":"价值直接同主体相联系，始终以主体为中心","c":"价值的存在取决于人们对它的认识和评价","d":"价值关系是实践的主体和客体相互作用关系中最根本的关系","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"AB","keyType":"多选","analyze":"本题考查的知识点是价值及其基本特征。价值是指在实践基础上形成的主体和客体之间的意义关系，是客体对个人、群体乃至整个社会的生活和活动所具有的积极意义。价值体现的是主体和客体之间的一种特定关系。价值离不开主体的需要，也离不开客体的特性。价值既具有主体性的特征，又具有客观基础。因此，本题的正确选项是AB。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":36868,"correctTimesAmount":11403,"accuracyAmount":30.9,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":0.0,"newKeyType":2,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":7,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["AB"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"多选","prname":"第一部分 马克思主义哲学原理>第四章 实践与认识及其发展规律","exerNum":null}]}}